txt.en: The fell Warg-rider, paired with his mount, is a terrifying foe, doubled in strength with his fanged companion bearing him upon his endeavours.
The great mount, paired with his master, harbours twice the strength of a mighty foe.
Gothghaash of the flowing fire knows no fear, for his wreath of flame lends him unnatural strength and cunning defences.
Defeat the villains of the Grand Stair.
Ilzkâl, guardian of the foyer of the Grand Stair, is a powerful Orc and cruel. He invites battle on his doorstep.
